{
  "stem": "12053.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we went to revisit as a group after the big 50-year reunion I organized in 1989.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we went there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that, for many people, it was the most traumatic, the most memorable time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because that was the first time we'd, we'd been to revisit the place of our arrival.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the actual huts still existed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They're still there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Or they were there a few years ago.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And a plaque has been put up to commemorate our arrival.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We saw to that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The mayor of Harwich saw to that a few years ago.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we were there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was quite an adventure, like I said.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We lived in those little huts.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My sister wasn't with me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My sister came six months later.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My friend and I shared a hut.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there were big dining halls.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was sort of a Butlins, a cheaper-- you know, a bit cheaper than Butlins.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was a big dining hall where we were made welcome.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And on a Saturday and Sunday, the weekend, we all called it the cattle market.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "People used to come from all over England and view us with a view of taking us to their homes and start a new life.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we should have been very grateful.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But we didn't feel very grateful, because it wasn't Very nice to be just picked and chosen by-- at random.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then a lot of children who weren't chosen, they were allocated homes to various people all over Britain.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It wasn't easy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It wasn't an easy time.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
